cu.explanation_en: Setting the PHY layer log level to an unknown enum 'unknown' will cause logging configuration failure and prevent proper system initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PHY layer log level to an unknown enum 'unknown' will cause logging configuration failure and prevent proper system initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PHY 層日誌等級設定為未知的枚舉值 'unknown'，會導致日誌配置失敗，並阻止正確的系統初始化。
